      "version": 134,
      "versionNonce": 803904903,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "text": "1) Functional Requirements\nDefine Objects\nThink Users: Product/App Teams • Operators/On-call • Platform/Admin\nPer user: configure • observe(who and what) • control\nExplicit v1 scope stated before architecture",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1) Functional Requirements\nDefine Objects\nThink Users: Product/App Teams • Operators/On-call • Platform/Admin\nPer user: configure • observe(who and what) • control\nExplicit v1 scope stated before architecture",
