    {
      "id": "tx3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 42.22009564218865,
      "y": 816.5515687421489,
      "width": 877.5332641601562,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 444,
      "versionNonce": 1920279713,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "text": "3) API Surface (actor-aware; control vs data plane)\nControl Plane (authoritative, durable): create/update/delete specs • submit/cancel work • config & quotas • ownership, audit, \n    Notes: idempotency notes per write and what to respond on duplicates, do not update/delete immutable objects\nData Plane (execute + read-only): execute/admit work • serve reads • health/readiness • emit metrics/logs/events\nAccess Model: all mutations via control plane; data plane is stateless, bounded, and never authoritative\nLifecycle Contract: spec → admit → execute → observe → terminate (success | failure | cancel)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3) API Surface (actor-aware; control vs data plane)\nControl Plane (authoritative, durable): create/update/delete specs • submit/cancel work • config & quotas • ownership, audit, \n    Notes: idempotency notes per write and what to respond on duplicates, do not update/delete immutable objects\nData Plane (execute + read-only): execute/admit work • serve reads • health/readiness • emit metrics/logs/events\nAccess Model: all mutations via control plane; data plane is stateless, bounded, and never authoritative\nLifecycle Contract: spec → admit → execute → observe → terminate (success | failure | cancel)",
