    {
      "id": "tx5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 41.80953126140599,
      "y": 1132.1546759002174,
      "width": 1032.6390380859375,
      "height": 87.50658121296838,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 407,
      "versionNonce": 1335534223,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "text": "5) High-Level Components & Flows (Boxes=ownership, Arrows=contracts, Flows=stories)\nComponents by responsibility: entry/interface • control/authority • execution/serving • state/durability • async delivery • observability • external deps.\nCore flows: change path (propose→authorize→persist) • execution path • reconcile/apply path • observe path • recover path.\nFlow annotations: authN/Z boundary • admission/quotas • correctness invariants • failure domain (blast radius, fail-open/closed) • visibility/SLOs.\n",
      "fontSize": 14.001052994074941,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5) High-Level Components & Flows (Boxes=ownership, Arrows=contracts, Flows=stories)\nComponents by responsibility: entry/interface • control/authority • execution/serving • state/durability • async delivery • observability • external deps.\nCore flows: change path (propose→authorize→persist) • execution path • reconcile/apply path • observe path • recover path.\nFlow annotations: authN/Z boundary • admission/quotas • correctness invariants • failure domain (blast radius, fail-open/closed) • visibility/SLOs.\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aA",
      "frameId": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1769093819948,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
