      "versionNonce": 629169761,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "text": "Assumptions (make falsifiable)\n Workload: RPS, payload, tenants/models\n Environment: single vs multi-region\n Data sensitivity: PII allowed? redaction?\n\nFailure test: “If this is wrong, which section \n    do I revisit—Scope, Invariants, or NFRs?”",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
