      "versionNonce": 2133800335,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "text": "Scope Gate (use before architecture)\nIN (v1): 5–8 bullets\nOUT (v1): 5–8 bullets\nRules:\n• don’t add features w/o business req\n• baseline vs later phases\n• if you expand, say it explicitly\n\nQuick check: “If I removed this, would the \nsystem still meet the business ask?”",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Scope Gate (use before architecture)\nIN (v1): 5–8 bullets\nOUT (v1): 5–8 bullets\nRules:\n• don’t add features w/o business req\n• baseline vs later phases\n• if you expand, say it explicitly\n\nQuick check: “If I removed this, would the \nsystem still meet the business ask?”",
